Convert example:

 $t = new pMagick('./rose.jpg',false);
 if ($t->resize('50%','images/rose_50.png')){
      print 'ok';
 } else {
     print 'error :\\';
 }

This example is equal to: shell# convert rose.jpg -resize 50% rose_59.png


Mogrify example:

 $t = new pMagick('./rose.jpg');
 if ($t->resize('50%'){
      print 'ok';
 } else {
     print 'error :\\';
 }
